hall.exhibit_highlights_en:
Huaweike Electronic Skin constructs full-body tactile perception for robots through a variety of sensing technologies, driving the evolution of robots from programmed operations to environment-adaptive intelligence.
-Hand Perception: Detects three-dimensional force signals, sliding states, surface texture features;
-Torso Perception: Collision detection, short-range perception;
-Foot Perception: Real-time acquisition of plantar center of pressure trajectory, ground reaction force, and torque.

-Products suitable for your application;
-Ensuring the quality of each product;
-Providing timely and globalized technical support and services.
